message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with signal processing and audio analysis. Other likely categories could be cs.LG (machine learning) as the paper proposes a method for training a deep learning system, cs.CL (computational linguistics) as the paper deals with audio event detection, cs.CV (computer vision) as the paper uses convolutional neural networks, and cs.AI (artificial intelligence) as the paper proposes a new loss function for weakly supervised learning.
